---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h2 style="text-align: center;">🧑‍💻 Ping from Suceava Hacks</h2>
			<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/suceavahacks/.github/refs/heads/main/svh.png" />
			<p>
				Welcome to our digital space! Here we post everything related to Suceava Hacks — announcements, recaps, ideas, and great moments from the community.
			</p>
			<p>
				Whether you attended an event and want to revisit photos, or you're looking for what we’re organizing next, this is the right place. It’s our logbook, but also a source of inspiration.
			</p>
			<h4>📅 What’s next</h4>
			<img src="https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/65bf43100a2dbf52a98e80cd52580bbbc7ed2e98_group_136.svg" />
			<ul>
				<li> 
				<strong>September 27-28, 2025</strong> <a href="https://daydream.hackclub.com" target="_blank">Daydream</a> – a 24-hour game jam organized in hundreds of cities worldwide!
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				<strong>And guess what? We’ll have amazing <a href="https://www.jukeboxprint.com/custom-stickers" target="_blank">custom stickers</a> from Jukebox to make the event even more special!</strong>
			</p>
			<h4>🎟️ How to join the community?</h4>
			<p>
				You don’t need a form to be part of Suceava Hacks. If you’re on <a href="https://discord.gg/qDPZXZAAyN" target="_blank">Discord</a> or <a href="https://hackclub.slack.com" target="_blank">Slack</a>, you’re already with us!
			</p>	
			<h4>🤝 Want to get involved?</h4>
			<p>
				We’re always happy when new people join us! You can write articles, help with organization, or come up with ideas for future events. Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/qDPZXZAAyN" target="_blank">Discord</a> and let’s talk.
			</p>
			<h4>💸 Support Suceava Hacks</h4>
			<p>
				Suceava Hacks is 100% organized by volunteers, and every hackathon or meetup means time, passion, and sometimes costs. If you want to support our community to grow and continue creating, you can make a donation. (Not tax-deductible in Romania.)
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="https://hcb.hackclub.com/svh" target="_blank">→ Donate here</a>
			</p>		
		</main>
</html>
